title: Best Of Scorpions
description:
This is a Best Of Scorpions Album from 1979
I have not been able to find this anywhere else including discography&#039;s
I compiled this album from my Mp3 collection as I am not able to play the 
record at the moment
The songs them selfs are available on various separate albums.
I have included pictures of the cover for the folder, and media player.
These are not available from any other source that I have looked at.
This is a great album if your a classic rock fan, or Scorpions pre 80&#039;s fan
Or if you have a collection Of Scorpions albums already and would like a rare
one to add to your collection.

Tracks Include:
 1. Steamrock Fever
 2. Pictured Life
 3. Robot Man
 4. Backstage Queen
 5. Speedy&#039;s Coming
 6. Hell Cat
 7. He&#039;s A Woman - She&#039;s A Man
 8. In Trance
 9. Dark Lady
10. The Sails Of Charon
11. Virgin Killer


Enjoy!!
